[6.16404, "o", "  \u001b[1mв”Ђв”Ђ Step 3: Conflict Detection в”Ђв”Ђ\u001b[0m\r\n  Two workers both editing src/auth.ts.\r\n"]
[6.164054, "o", "  Native Agent Teams: 'break work so each owns different files'\r\n  Lead System: detects it BEFORE the collision.\r\n\r\n"]
[6.164619, "o", "  \u001b[33m> coord_detect_conflicts session=alpha files=[src/auth.ts]\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[6.165478, "o", "## CONFLICTS DETECTED\r\n\r\n### Session Overlaps\r\n- **beta2222** (undefined): src/auth.ts вЂ” \"Write tests\"\r\n\r\n**Recommendation:** Coordinate before editing these files.\r\n\r\n"]
[9.166302, "o", "  \u001b[1mв”Ђв”Ђ Step 4: Direct worker messaging в”Ђв”Ђ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
